{"tid":1851072,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗ig突破2億追隨者冠全球","createTime":"2020-01-30T01:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T10:03:29.000Z","uid":12628,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa417dc089a2de8dfce6a9f07996c113a7259d7","tid":1851072,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://twofoottalk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/tenor-3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwofoottalk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Ftenor-3.gif&h=6ed64481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祖雲達斯巨星基斯坦奴朗拿度成為史上第1位Instagram追隨者突破2億的人。<br />\n祖雲達斯鋒將基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）是超越一眾名人，諸如Ariana Grande（1.72億）、Selena Gomez（1.66億）、Beyonce（1.38億）等，位列Instagram追隨者數目榜首，放諸球壇亦比美斯及尼馬為多，足證其在網絡的影響力。 C朗也發帖文紀錄這個里程碑：「Wow 2億！感情每一位與我每天分享這個旅程。」文尾還加上拍掌及心心的符號。 除了在ig宣傳自己品牌的產品外，C朗也藉此宣傳贊助商品，<span style=\"color: orange;\">根據市場公司Hopper HQ評估，C朗每出一個獲贊助的帖子，約可獲得90萬歐元的回報，令他每年在這方面的收入達4800萬歐元，比他在祖雲達斯的薪酬還要高，簡言之好過踢波。</span>"},{"pid":"3e41eb4c57308236bd2a00aba289ba3c68c90ea4","tid":1851072,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"雞姦犯都咁受歡迎..."},{"pid":"9329be22ebea8bb7eac48ee009fe1b1aa8f3ee29","tid":1851072,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e41eb4c57308236bd2a00aba289ba3c68c90ea4","tid":1851072,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"雞姦犯都咁受歡迎..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dee1250f290340a7bf215f498f57b96fb215814","tid":1851072,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"蛆啲波糧都夠晒牙朗打雞姦官司，ig賺啲錢，又夠埋手下個目標"},{"pid":"4459bcf1a3938b8779c3335763e7858d61572e5d","tid":1851072,"uid":127033,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2dee1250f290340a7bf215f498f57b96fb215814","tid":1851072,"uid":12628,"like"